N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 1750.14 - Commissioner's certification

State Regulations

Upon receipt of the documentation required hereunder and
the payment of the fees as set forth in section
1750.13
of this Part, and upon
receipt of a conformed copy of the proposed certificate of dissolution, the
division shall issue a certification to the Secretary of State stating that the
requirements of the Private Housing Finance Law have been complied with and
that the division has no objection to the filing by the housing company of the
certificate of dissolution. Notes
